{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037", "id": 562752658, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU1NjI3NTI2NTg=", "number": 69037, "title": "Smarter derive(Default) for PhantomData", "user": {"login": "ark0f", "id": 21154701, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIxMTU0NzAx", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/21154701?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f", "html_url": "https://github.com/ark0f", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ark0f/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2020-02-10T18:40:41Z", "updated_at": "2020-02-10T18:41:58Z", "closed_at": "2020-02-10T18:41:58Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "```rust\r\nuse std::marker::PhantomData;\r\n\r\nstruct TypeWithoutDefault;\r\n\r\n#[derive(Default)]\r\nstruct NewType<T>(PhantomData<T>);\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let _ = NewType::<TypeWithoutDefault>::default();\r\n    // ^ E0599\r\n    // no function or associated item named `default` found \r\n    // for type `NewType<TypeWithoutDefault>` in the current scope\r\n}\r\n```\r\nBut if we implement `Default` without derive:\r\n```rust\r\nimpl<T> Default for NewType<T> {\r\n    fn default() -> Self {\r\n        Self(PhantomData)\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nThen code compiles successfully.\r\n\r\nCan `derive(Default)` be smarter for cases like this?", "closed_by": {"login": "jonas-schievink", "id": 1786438, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3ODY0Mzg=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1786438?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink", "html_url": "https://github.com/jonas-schievink", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jonas-schievink/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/69037/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}